message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely sub-category as it deals with sound and audio processing. cs.LG is also likely as it deals with machine learning and deep learning. cs.HC is another possible sub-category as it deals with human-computer interaction and perception. cs.NE is also possible as it deals with neural networks and their applications. cs.CL is less likely as it deals with natural language processing, which is not directly related to the topic of this paper.
